TỔNG QUAN BÀI HỌC
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

  Giảng viên : Matt
  Chủ đề     : Cloud Security
  Mục tiêu   : 6 lĩnh vực chính


NỘI DUNG CHÍNH
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

  • Identity and Access Management (IAM)
      • Identity (provisioning, centralized directory)
      • Authentication (username/password, MFA)
      • Authorization (level of access)
      • Privileged Identity Management (PIM)

  • Data Security
      • Data at Rest (encryption)
      • Data in Transit (SSL/TLS)
      • Cryptography & Key Management
      • Remote Backups, Sanitization

  • Network Security
      • Virtual Private Cloud (VPC)
      • Network Perimeter
      • Virtual Switches, Firewalls
      • Network Security Groups

  • Compute-based Security
      • Hypervisors, VMs
      • OS, Middleware, Runtime
      • Inventory Management

  • Application Security
      • Standard Applications
      • Microservices, APIs
      • Containers, Serverless

  • Security Monitoring and Policy
      • Monitoring & Alerting
      • Auditing
      • Incident Response
      • Policy and Governance


KẾT LUẬN
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

  Cloud Security bao gồm IAM, data, network, compute, application và monitoring/policy. 

  Áp dụng multi-layer security là chìa khóa để bảo vệ tài nguyên cloud.


